text: Poliaenus oregonus is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by John Lawrence LeConte in 1861. It is known from North America.BioLib.cz - Poliaenus oregonus. Retrieved 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Pogonocherini Category:Beetles described in 1861
title: Poliaenus oregonus
